✅ Gunakan bot sewajarnya & hormati sesama member

🤖 Powered by Arsena Official Store</div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert a-info">
      <strong>💡 Cara Kirim</strong>
      Copy teks → buka grup WA kamu → paste & kirim → screenshot untuk bukti ke owner.
    </div>

    <button class="btn btn-p" onclick="goStep(3)">Sudah Dikirim →</button>
    <button class="btn btn-g" onclick="goStep(1)">← Kembali</button>
  </div>

  <!-- STEP 3 -->
